## DNS

nameservers configuration is in `/etc/resolver`, e.g. for the `.dev` domain, configure nameserver like this:

```c
# /etc/resolver/dev
nameserver 127.0.0.1
#nameserver 8.8.8.8 # additional stuff example
```

own DNS server:

```sh-session
brew install dnsmasq
# restart:
sudo brew services restart dnsmasq
```
